{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/GameImage4.png?t=1738147664\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/jietu4.png?t=1738147664\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/jietu9.png?t=1738147664\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a single player action adventure game that includes mythological themed character actions and role-playing,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use regular attacks and skills, spells, such as magic, celestial phenomena, and body fixing spells, to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight and defeat the enemies you encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[h2] Gameplay Introduction [/h2]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. Basic operation: Use the keyboard and mouse (gamepad) to control the player's hero, embark on a game journey, and control the player</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move, jump, change of perspective, attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. Spell skill release: Use the keyboard (gamepad) to specify keys to release skills and spells, such as clone summoning</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clone attacks on enemies, use body fixing techniques to control enemy behavior, and use the magic of celestial phenomena and earth skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">to increase the player's character's attack by doubling their own size Power effect, instant movement skill to evade enemy attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. Upgrade System: Eliminate a specified number of enemies, which can increase the player's hero level, health, attack power, and spells</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skill effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 Enemy AI: Intelligent enemy AI enables enemies to have intelligent jumping, healing, and other AI functions, providing a superior gaming </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[h2] Excellent graphics [/2]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Developed using UE5, making the characters and game scenes incredibly realistic, achieving advanced game graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">[h2] Hero Skills [/2]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use different spell skills to match game characters and achieve different gaming experiences.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738147664","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/page.bg.jpg?t=1738147664","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/2e0249d13b42090ce4f8b66ad0e321d4f66518fd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738147664","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/2e0249d13b42090ce4f8b66ad0e321d4f66518fd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738147664","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/GameImage4.png?t=1738147664\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/jietu4.png?t=1738147664\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3415280/extras/jietu9.png?t=1738147664\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a single player action adventure game that includes mythological themed character actions and role-playing,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use regular attacks and skills, spells, such as magic, celestial phenomena, and body fixing spells, to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight and defeat the enemies you encounter